org.eclipse.mat.hprof.extension

Interface IParsingEnhancer


  • public interface IParsingEnhancer
    This interface provides the possibility to perform some actions and add information the a parsed snapshot, just after the parsing of an HPROF file is done. Thus if there is a file separate from the HPROF file which provides additional information, an implementor of this interface can attach this additional information to the snapshot See the documentation on the org.eclipse.mat.hprof.enhancer extension point
